{"tid":1791765,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【好愛國】伊能靜微博播囡囡清唱《我愛北京天安門》 台網民大叫嘔心","createTime":"2019-12-21T06:10:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T12:35:40.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"60f7c4548fc5ef72741512147ecb36ce65354c2b","tid":1791765,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T06:10:55.000Z","msg":"台灣藝人伊能靜2015年後與大陸藝人秦昊再婚後生下囡囡小米粒，現年已經3歲。婚後伊能靜與家人在大陸定居，但偶爾她也會返台灣探親。<br />\n日前被傳媒拍得在台北逛街的伊能靜，昨晚不但在微博表態說自己是中國人，而且更指女兒小米粒喜歡唱《我愛北京天安門》。伊能靜在微博留言：「直播的時候被問過你是哪裡人，這個問題很可愛，我是中國人。祖籍山東濟南，父輩的血，山東人的個性，真的埋在骨肉裡。米粒最喜歡的歌，是《我愛北京天安門》。一家人不說兩家話，聽聽米粒的聲音多可愛。」。<br />\n伊能靜更上載囡囡唱歌的錄音聲帶，聽到小米粒在唱：「我愛北京天安門，天安門上太陽升，偉大領袖毛主席，指引我們向前進......」不少台灣網民看到相關新聞後留言大叫「嘔心」、「放棄台灣國籍啊」，也有網民表示：「尊重你的選擇，記得健保要拋棄，不要跟黃安一樣噁心的回台看病。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191221/large/1576904240_53d6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191221%2Flarge%2F1576904240_53d6.jpg&h=fd19f203&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191221/large/1576902551_7252.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191221%2Flarge%2F1576902551_7252.jpg&h=23dd253e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191221/60402578\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191221%2F60402578&d=Wr%2FXdV%2FekiVpClOitW4NQSNNnhsiPIcvur842Fp1uB0%3D&h=df805865\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191221%2F60402578&h=deb3b992\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191221/60402578</a>"},{"pid":"a7463d7be0d71616db6b53c40732b6da1c60e149","tid":1791765,"uid":99568,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"r